# Binderbase — code ownership.
#
# Syntax: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-security/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Each line is: <path pattern>  <@owner> [<@owner> ...]
# The last matching pattern wins, so more specific rules go at the bottom.
#
# Note: CODEOWNERS assignment only *requests* review. It does not block merge
# unless branch protection is configured to "Require review from Code Owners"
# (see docs/OPERATIONS.md).

# Default owner for anything not matched below.
